In between classes, you can find me listening to Mitski, Chappell Roan, and Kendrick Lamar, but recently I've been exploring Childish Gambino's earlier albums as well.

I'm a part of UCBUGG and AFA, and I'll be sure to advertise those clubs to you if you have any interest in animation or storytelling as a whole. I would call myself a certified Thai Basil fan, but honestly I more often find myself at the Chipotle on Telegraph (you can't beat $11 for a bowl).
